author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at a phenomenon posted by Josh Strike Hayes, a popular channel who's looked into the viewership drop reported sitewide. It's credible to believe the reason behind this is actually a problem caused by adblockers which is actually now harming the creator far more than they originally did, this all can be avoided if the site itself wasn't becoming so annoying to use. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Adblockers Are Really Hurting YouTube Now...
